Class AutoDeleteMVBTree

java.lang.Object
  xxl.core.indexStructures.Tree
      xxl.core.indexStructures.BPlusTree

              xxl.core.indexStructures.AutoDeleteMVBTree

public class AutoDeleteMVBTree
extends MVBTree

This class extends the MVBTree with auto-delete functionality, i.e. objects have to be inserted with a deletion version and will be automatically deleted at that version.
